Lio: That's not the case! Sis is, she's definitely...
Lio: She's so mad that she doesn't want to forgive me anymore!
Nigel: Sighs~ So, what does that have to do with you coming here to the Bears' caves?
Lio: Well, you see... there are a lot of shiny things around here, right...
Lio: Cin told me that all girls like shiny things...
Nigel: That's probably just her personal taste though...

Lio: Besides, I heard Sis Angel talk about the Moonstones in this cave. She said that they will illuminate only during this time of the year,
and it's a rare sight to behold!
Nigel: It's really dangerous here. You shouldn't listen to her babbling...
Bear Soldier: You damn illegal miners!!!

Nigel: Tch, I'll handle it from here!
Nigel: Lio, you leave first! We'll meet up outside the cave entrance!
Lio: Understood! Nigel, be careful yourself!!
Bear Soldier: Grrrr! You're not getting away!
Lio: So pretty! Could it be that these are the rumored Moonstones!?
Lio: I wonder if sis will like this?
